::Rex::

Rex frowns as he watches a strange floating face in front of Gangon, his 
widening as he sees the bars of Gangon's cell burst. He swears, setting the 
defences on alert.

"Computer, scan for anomalies," he says, the computer giving it's reports a 
second later. It was strange, like nothing Rex had ever seen before. He 
orders the computer to fully analize it, and figure out how to destroy it, 
and then turns to Gangon.

"Any idea of what's going on?" he asks, holding his gun ready.
